data.description: Welcome to Fairway Cove! This beautiful community in MetroWest has quick access to MetroWest’s Golf Course, Florida’s Turnpike, I-4, SR408, and tons of shopping & dining. Enjoy weekends riding rollercoasters and drinking Butterbeer at Universal Studios & Islands of Adventure, or shop ‘til you drop at the Mall at Millenia. NEW ROOF 2021 . This beautiful home stands on a large corner lot with lush landscaping overlooking the tranquil pond across the street. This home is re-piped meaning no polybutylene pipes to worry about. Inside you’ll be greeted by vaulted ceilings NEW SKYLIGHTS 2021 and highly polished dark wood laminate flooring. The family room features NEW CUSTOM BUILT SHELVING 2021, a wet bar (ideal for entertaining), wood-burning fireplace, transom windows that bathe the space in natural light and French door access to the screened lanai. Retreat to the private backyard oasis, presenting a heated pool with fun water feature, koi pond, expansive lanai, secure child safety fence, and spacious yard. The kitchen boasts plenty of counters and cabinet space, island and generous sized eat-in nook overlooking the pool. Unique 2/2 split bedroom plan. Your spacious master bedroom has private pool access, room for a sitting area and an oversized walk-in closet. Master bathroom and NEW SHOWER 2021 and NEW VANITY 2023.  On the same side as the master suite is the second bedroom and a full bath – ideal to set up as an office or nursery. Call today and schedule a private showing.
